{"tid":595545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用電量激增 紐約電力局將對掘礦公司加收電費","createTime":"2018-03-16T17:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T02:52:36.000Z","uid":66943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc92a6457dfe2b4df83435581a99dbca1e1b30c","tid":595545,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"紐約公共服務委員會上周四宣布，該機構已經批准紐約市政電力局（New York Municipal Power Agency）對試圖利用該州低成本水電來開採數字貨幣的礦商漲價。紐約市政電力局透露，在部分情況下，數字貨幣掘礦公司的用電量能佔據一家市政電力部門需求的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/03/20180316_zq_281_14/gamersky_02origin_03_201831614561ED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F03%2F20180316_zq_281_14%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_201831614561ED.jpg&h=3eb05f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lunalife.ru/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/joint_mininng_project_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flunalife.ru%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fjoint_mininng_project_1.jpg&h=64dabda2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，同樣由於用電量激增，美國普拉茨堡也正考慮禁止該市的Bitcon掘礦活動。據當地電力部門透露，普拉茨堡市至少有兩家虛擬貨幣礦商，它們的用電功率達到了 11.2 MW。不過電力部門也表示，過去數月當地用電激增也可能是由於寒冷天氣造成的正常季節波動。"},{"pid":"45f62c872de56b5cf12c76509ad39951c8f6615d","tid":595545,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"等睇右膠撐嘥電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bc00fb341644e734558431ddac52fdcd13c35f","tid":595545,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"誇張"},{"pid":"961e1fc1a298887902e01837be372f7e44fcc41f","tid":595545,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T22:23:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"fcc635243fff7ad92379049b55820f0d85d8e712","tid":595545,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T22:28:54.000Z","msg":"等睇bitcon爆破"},{"pid":"49